@startuml
title NetRT Conceptual Architecture

!theme plain
skinparam componentStyle rectangle
skinparam packageStyle rectangle

package "Ingestion Layer" {
    [DICOM Listener Service] as Listener
    note right of Listener: Handles C-ECHO, C-STORE\nManages Network Associations
}

package "Data Management Layer" {
    [File System Manager] as FSM
    [Study Debouncer] as Debouncer
    database "Temporary Storage" as Storage
    note right of Storage: Organized by StudyUID\nSegregated (DCM vs Structure)
}

package "Processing Core" {
    [Study Orchestrator] as Orch
    
    frame "Processing Pipelines" {
        [Anonymization Engine] as Anon
        [Contour Processor] as Contouring
        [Burn-in / Overlay Engine] as BurnIn
    }
}

package "Output Layer" {
    [Report Generator] as Report
    [DICOM Sender Service] as Sender
}

[External Modalities] --> Listener : Push Images (C-STORE)
Listener --> FSM : Request Save
FSM --> Storage : Write Files
Storage ..> Debouncer : File System Events
Debouncer --> Orch : Trigger "Study Ready"

Orch --> FSM : Load Data
Orch --> Anon : 1. Anonymize PII
Orch --> Contouring : 2. Generate Contours/Masks
Orch --> BurnIn : 3. Create Visual Overlays
Orch --> Report : 4. Generate Audit Report

Sender <-- Orch : Dispatch Results
Sender --> [Remote PACS/VNA] : C-STORE Results

@enduml
